# Ensure C++ files are classified correctly
*.cpp linguist-detectable
*.h linguist-detectable
*.hpp linguist-detectable

# Ignore other language files
*.i linguist-vendored
*.swig linguist-vendored
*.c linguist-vendored
Makefile linguist-vendored
*.mk linguist-vendored
*.cmake linguist-vendored
CMakeLists.txt linguist-vendored
CMakeFiles linguist-vendored
